other_locations > computer > etc > default > grub (text file)

line number 11 comes like -> GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX=""
in double quotes you have to add nouveau.modeset=0 : LIKE THIS ->
GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX="nouveau.modeset=0"

cmd :- sudo update-grub
